MODIFICATIONS
================================================================================

The following modifications have been made by the maintainers of this fork
(the "Modifier") as a Proof of Concept (POC) to evaluate Apollo Router
Enterprise capabilities prior to purchasing an Enterprise license:

1. Enterprise feature gating logic has been modified to allow internal
   evaluation of all router capabilities without an active license key.

2. Certain test cases related to license enforcement have been removed
   as they are no longer applicable to the modified behavior.

Files modified:
- apollo-router/src/uplink/license_enforcement.rs
- apollo-router/src/state_machine.rs
- apollo-router/src/axum_factory/axum_http_server_factory.rs

